      "comment_id" : 88420355,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "I am running an OpenJDK JVM, version 1.8.0u171 (Debian 9), and it seems to accept the <code>-XX:-OmitStackTraceInFastThrow</code> flag as well. I&#39;ve yet to confirm if that was why I was also failing to print stack-traces (e.g., using <code>e.printStackTrace</code>), but it seems highly likely. I&#39;ve expanded the answer to reflect this discovery."
    }, {
