      "comment_id" : 139654407,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "As a tip, the stack trace will be shown until the JIT decides to recompile an optimized version of the function, so if trying to diagnose the issue, look for log entries shortly after starting or deploying the application, and those entries may have stack traces."
